<h2 class="blog--title">
<a href="/blog/2014/04/01/first-milestone-of-spring-data-release-train-dijkstra-available">First Milestone of Spring Data Release Train Dijkstra Available</a>
</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
<div class="meta-data--item desktop-only">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon releases"></div>
<a class="category" href="/blog/category/releases">Releases</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<img class="meta-data--icon" src="https://gravatar.com/avatar/977c74bb044a9d4fa90b305824eda390?s=20&amp;d=mm" />
<a class="author" href="/team/ogierke">Oliver Drotbohm</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon calendar"></div>
<time class="date" pubdate="" datetime="2014-04-01 11:39:30.76">April 1, 2014</time>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon comments"></div>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="1472" href="/blog/2014/04/01/first-milestone-of-spring-data-release-train-dijkstra-available#disqus_thread">
</a></div>
</header>
<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p>I am excited to announce the availability of the first milestone of the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edsger_W._Dijkstra">Dijkstra</a> release train of the Spring Data umbrella project. This train iteration is a very special one as we have 5 new modules joining the release train: Spring Data <a href="https://projects.spring.io/spring-data-couchbase/">Couchbase</a>, <a href="https://projects.spring.io/spring-data-cassandra/">Cassandra</a>, <a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-data-elasticsearch">Elasticsearch</a>, <a href="https://projects.spring.io/spring-data-gemfire/">Gemfire</a> and <a href="https://projects.spring.io/spring-data-redis/">Redis</a>. I am even more excited about that as the majority of them are community lead projects. These are the modules included:</p>
<ul>
<li>Spring Data Build 1.4 M1 - <a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-data-build/issues?milestone=15&amp;state=closed">Changelog</a></li>
<li>Spring Data Commons 1.8 M1 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-milestone/org/springframework/data/spring-data-commons/1.8.0.M1">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/commons/docs/1.8.0.M1/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/commons/docs/1.8.0.M1/reference/htmlsingle">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/commons/docs/1.8.0.M1/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
<li>Spring Data JPA 1.6 M1 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-milestone/org/springframework/data/spring-data-jpa/1.6.0.M1">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/jpa/docs/1.6.0.M1/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/jpa/docs/1.6.0.M1/reference/htmlsingle">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/jpa/docs/1.6.0.M1/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
<li>Spring Data MongoDB 1.5 M1 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-milestone/org/springframework/data/spring-data-mongodb/1.5.0.M1">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/mongodb/docs/1.5.0.M1/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/mongodb/docs/1.5.0.M1/reference/htmlsingle">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/mongodb/docs/1.5.0.M1/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
<li>Spring Data Neo4j 3.1 M1 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-milestone/org/springframework/data/spring-data-neo4j/3.1.0.M1">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/neo4j/docs/3.1.0.M1/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/neo4j/docs/3.1.0.M1/reference/htmlsingle">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/neo4j/docs/3.1.0.M1/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
<li>Spring Data Solr 1.2 M1 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-milestone/org/springframework/data/spring-data-solr/1.2.0.M1">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/solr/docs/1.2.0.M1/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/solr/docs/1.2.0.M1/reference/htmlsingle">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/solr/docs/1.2.0.M1/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
<li>Spring Data Couchbase 1.1 M1 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-milestone/org/springframework/data/spring-data-couchbase/1.1.0.M1">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/couchbase/docs/1.1.0.M1/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/couchbase/docs/1.1.0.M1/reference/htmlsingle">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/couchbase/docs/1.1.0.M1/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
<li>Spring Data Cassandra 1.0 M1 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-milestone/org/springframework/data/spring-data-cassandra/1.0.0.M1">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/cassandra/docs/1.0.0.M1/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/cassandra/docs/1.0.0.M1/reference/htmlsingle">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/cassandra/docs/1.0.0.M1/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
<li>Spring Data Elasticsearch 1.0 M2 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-milestone/org/springframework/data/spring-data-elasticsearch/1.0.0.M2">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/elasticsearch/docs/1.0.0.M2/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/elasticsearch/docs/1.0.0.M2/reference/htmlsingle">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/elasticsearch/docs/1.0.0.M2/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
<li>Spring Data Gemfire 1.4 M1 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-milestone/org/springframework/data/spring-data-gemfire/1.4.0.M1">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/gemfire/docs/1.4.0.M1/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/gemfire/docs/1.4.0.M1/reference/htmlsingle">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/gemfire/docs/1.4.0.M1/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
<li>Spring Data Redis 1.3 M1 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-milestone/org/springframework/data/spring-data-redis/1.3.0.M1">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/redis/docs/1.3.0.M1/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/redis/docs/1.3.0.M1/reference/htmlsingle">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/redis/docs/1.3.0.M1/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
<li>Spring Data REST 2.1 M1 - <a href="https://repo.spring.io/libs-milestone/org/springframework/data/spring-data-rest-webmvc/2.1.0.M1">Artifacts</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/rest/docs/2.1.0.M1/api">JavaDocs</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/rest/docs/2.1.0.M1/reference/htmlsingle">Documentation</a> - <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/rest/docs/2.1.0.M1/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
